{"tid":362444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本總領事館指走私黃金案創新高　涉案港人增加","createTime":"2017-08-17T02:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T06:55:26.000Z","uid":13468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"29020662cac48d298689adf02e7925ffb6f73e4d","tid":362444,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T02:30:22.000Z","msg":"日本總領事館指走私黃金案創新高　涉案港人增加<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1348528-20170816.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1348528-20170816.htm&d=UlEy9l6EmTdir9krYDVFQZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=0619fe50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1348528-20170816.htm&h=c87c4c50\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1348528-20170816.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n香港本月初發生懷疑運金失竊案，一名商人報稱提供9千元酬勞及旅費予一個家庭，代為運送過百萬的黃金到日本，但其後失竊。<br />\n<br />\n日本駐港總領事館回覆本台查詢時表示，2015年7月至2016年6月期間，日本有294宗涉及走私黃金的案件，逃稅金額超過6億日圓，分別是前一年同期的1.7倍和2.6倍，創紀錄新高。<br />\n<br />\n總領事館說，這近300宗案件涉及468名罪犯，當中71名是香港人，按年多44人，走私黃金的主要輸出地區是香港。半數以上走私人士用束腹衣等將黃金縛於身上，或收藏在褲子的隱蔽口袋中。另外還有人收藏黃金在電腦電池、經加工的服飾，或收藏於人體內。<br />\n<br />\n總領事館指，若以隱瞞事實申告，或以虛假申告等不正當方式，攜帶黃金入境日本逃稅，最高可被判監禁10年或罰款1千萬日圓等。"},{"pid":"c6367d795146edefd2c7ab13fcb579f7c5aac90c","tid":362444,"uid":38523,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T02:42:32.000Z","msg":"早排天水圍一家都差d4件啦<br />\n一日百五件支那狗變成香港人<br />\n走私又可以入香港人數<br />\n配合埋支那狗唱衰香港人<br />\n一絕"},{"pid":"0200b6056ac2396a21c1e781c08fccfb6a01637d","tid":362444,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T02:43:23.000Z","msg":"仲唔取消港人免簽入日本 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ae618198ba58a4f55ca46e5d1b01b91575a2c9","tid":362444,"uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T02:53:06.000Z","msg":"「免費去日本三日兩夜，包埋酒店機票，只要帶兩條金條，就有千幾蚊水腳賺，好多後生仔爭住做」。有參與運金生意的阿偉向《蘋果》記者稱，不少「行家」近年都會在網上招攬想去日本、韓國旅遊的年輕人，湊夠人後便會組團出發，只要每人帶兩條各重1公斤的金條成功入境日本，便可免費旅行，還能賺到零用錢。由於港、日兩地的黃金差價每公斤逾3萬元，故不少人投身運金行業，最誇張每次可組織10多人運金，是名副其實的「運金團」。"},{"pid":"02e786e286263d4673e8a89072005663e9d83cbc","tid":362444,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T02:55:40.000Z","msg":"拉晒d港豬去打靶啦"},{"pid":"dda538a6f21db0058152a04af2783831d946bc14","tid":362444,"uid":38523,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T03:00:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拉晒d港豬去打靶啦</blockquote><br />\n拉得晒？<br />\n一日百五隻支那狗變身香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"551ea8e5789b9ca64777b4f6d1edbdbad85748e8","tid":362444,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T03:02:11.000Z","msg":"諗起泰國運毒三廢青<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/06/150135_7a80fe32d2508158ee7bd2a8c46cee40.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F06%2F150135_7a80fe32d2508158ee7bd2a8c46cee40.jpg&h=8c40e169&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d763279f7696fcd3676b8dde1c8dedbca477fe0d","tid":362444,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:44:57.000Z","msg":"好多後生做"},{"pid":"8a32e620d854a3d2a5acac5e984d2d4a73cc165b","tid":362444,"uid":36995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T06:50:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲唔取消港人免簽入日本 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n爽 連登仔無得奶日了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23dabcde7e68b8fbb4243dfb39ba023b28d41aa5","tid":362444,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T06:54:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗起泰國運毒三廢青<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/06/150135_7a80fe32d2508158ee7bd2a8c46cee40.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F06%2F150135_7a80fe32d2508158ee7bd2a8c46cee40.jpg&h=8c40e169&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地幾時上庭？好擔心"},{"pid":"e11c6b49c4e0c8cb57952c84b4930ac0b1dd1d8f","tid":362444,"uid":128600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T06:55:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多後生做</blockquote><br />\n免費旅遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}